            <h2>Trivia</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Beagles have one of the best senses of smell among dog breeds.</li>
                <li>They are often used in <b>search-and-rescue missions</b> and detection jobs.</li>
                <li>Beagles are <i>friendly, curious, and merry</i>, making them great family pets.</li>
